{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_53_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 どちらも白石でしょう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――九月二十六日　昼",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "（まさか、番組でお誕生日のお祝いをして）\n（もらえるなんて。本当にびっくりしちゃった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10233.333333400002,
          "startTime": 16.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11033.333333400002,
          "startTime": 17.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんがセットしてくれた髪も）\n（褒めてもらえたし。ふふ、素敵な誕生日だわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃーん、失礼します～\nそれと、お誕生日おめでとぉ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.000000000001,
          "startTime": 24.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん……！　ありがとうございます。そういえば\n今日はレギュラー番組の収録があるって言ってましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。後、沙季ちゃんに聞きたいことがあってな\nプレゼント贈ろうと思うんやけど、何がいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "他の子と被ってもあれかなーって、当日まで\n待ってたんよ。後、遠慮すんのはなしやで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……さ、先回りされてしまいました……\nでは、ええと……そうだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんのお話って、いつも面白いですよね\n私も何か、話にユーモアを織り交ぜたいんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、アドバイスがほしいってことやね\nふふ、そんくらい誕生日やなくても相談に乗るけどなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、せやなぁ……沙季ちゃんって知的やん？\nユーモアも、知的な方向がいいと思うんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、『なぞかけ』を入れてみるとか。山登りと\nかけまして、月のテンペストとときます、みたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "山登りと、月のテンペスト……その共通点……？\nハッ！　どちらも『の』がありますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "あー……ちゃ……ちゃうねん\nなぞかけって、そういうことやなくてな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも、『やまのぼり』の『の』と\n『つきのてんぺすと』の『の』で文字が共通してますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.338443299999,
          "startTime": 121.10000511
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ずばり、そのこころは\nどちらも同じ文字があるでしょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃうねん、伝わってる上でちゃうねん！\n言い換えとかやねん。どちらも『すず』が不可欠とかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "熊避けの鈴と、すずちゃんのすず……なるほど\nでは、沙季とかけまして、千紗とときます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "そのこころは\nどちらも、白石でしょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_53_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "いやだからなんもかかってないやん！？\n……けど、こういう天然なとこは逆におもろいんかもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}